# GameStore Frontend (Quick Start)

## Requirements
- Node.js v18.x or v20.x
- npm (v9+)

## Setup
1. `npm install`
2. Create `.env.local` with:
   - `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://your-api-url`
3. `npm run dev` (for development)
4. `npm run build && npm start` (for production)

## Auth
- Uses cookies for JWT auth
- Protected routes redirect to `/login`

## Ignored by git
- node_modules, .next, .out, /build
- .env*, .DS_Store, log files, .vercel, *.tsbuildinfo 